.ecl-contextual-navigation__list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; }
#globan .wt-globan--invalid-domain { background: rgb(255, 214, 23); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); padding: 5px 16px; text-align: center; }
#globan .wt-globan--center { background: rgb(238, 238, 238); display: flex; align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
#globan .wt-globan--content { display: flex; align-items: center; position: relative; }

#globan .wt-globan--button { text-decoration: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); font-weight: 400; margin: 0px 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px 7px; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; cursor: pointer; outline: none; border: 3px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); white-space: nowrap; }
#globan .wt-globan--button:hover { background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 68, 148); }
#globan .wt-globan--button[aria-expanded="true"], #globan .wt-globan--button:focus-visible { background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(255, 214, 23); color: rgb(0, 68, 148); }

#globan .wt-globan--dropdown { background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 0px; max-width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 4px 5px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); }
#globan .wt-globan--promo-container { background: rgb(0, 42, 153); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; z-index: 1; }
#globan .wt-globan--promo-content { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 16px 32px; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 1368px; }

#globan .wt-globan--promo-link { margin: 0px 0px 0px auto; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; align-items: center; outline: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; padding: 0px 20px; height: 44px; line-height: 28px; white-space: nowrap; border-radius: 2px; }

#globan .wt-globan--promo-container.dark .wt-globan--promo-link:hover, #globan .wt-globan--promo-container.dark .wt-globan--promo-link:focus-visible { background: rgb(0, 0, 46); outline: rgb(0, 70, 255) solid 2px; outline-offset: 2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; }
#globan .wt-globan--promo-container img, #globan .wt-globan--promo-container canvas { position: absolute; inset: 0px; z-index: 1; width: 100%; height: 100%; }
#globan .wt-globan--promo-container img { left: 50%; top: 50%; height: auto; min-height: 100%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: auto; max-width: 100%; }

#globan .wt-globan--promo-link { margin: 0px 0px 0px auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 46); text-decoration: none; border: 0px; display: flex; align-items: center; outline: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; padding: 0px 12px; white-space: nowrap; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); position: absolute; right: 20px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; height: 100%; border-radius: 0px; }
#globan .wt-globan--content { display: flex; align-items: center; width: 100%; padding: 0px !important; }
